    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">You can, by the way, always add two known, equal-weight islanders to any weigh-in, one on either side, just to get more people involved or come up with an alternate solution, as you like. Now, yes, I’m aware that the show itself put out a video of Captain Holt himself announcing the solution, but the solution is both flawed and incomplete; see if you can spot it:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
